g.text: A feature with no strings means it does not have any dependencies
This feature cannot be delivered until multiple teams complete their dependencies
A milestone or event is occurring in iteration 1.3 (e.g., release, trade show)
Red strings (or lines for digital boards) are used to connect a feature or milestone to one or more dependencies. Sometimes a dependency has its own dependencies (see Lions in iteration 1.2)
